# LINKEDIN OAUTH (Required for LinkedIn Account Linking)
# ===========================================================================
#
# How to get LinkedIn API credentials:
#
# 1. Go to: https://www.linkedin.com/developers/
# 2. Create a new app
# 3. Go to "Auth" tab
# 4. Copy "Client ID" and "Client Secret"
# 5. Add redirect URI:
